  "id": "RAW_5fbcd1f3",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-18）：字节联合港中文推出 Video As Prompt，以混合变压器架构实现可控视频生成飞跃",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500456&idx=1&sn=b83561cfe40d1e239ec812a13a317ebc",
  "date": "2025-11-18 09:23:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Video-As-Prompt</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3574074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"416\" data-imgfileid=\"100016796\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9ae39328&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXSGAIeiatOiajozNgUxQF6rPaVG95jDJaiaibNzITAyPunQWQzIwFu4tz8Qv81picfN9rqtibvzyicSqfw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Video-As-Prompt (VAP) 是首个统一的语义视频生成模型。其核心思想是通过一个具有目标语义的参考视频作为提示，来生成具有相同语义的动画视频。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">VAP 采用了一种新的范式，将统一且可泛化的语义控制视频生成重新定义为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">上下文生成</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该模型利用参考视频作为直接的语义提示，通过一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">即插即用的混合变压器专家</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">指导冻结的视频扩散变压器 (DiT)。这种架构避免了灾难性遗忘，并通过时间偏置位置嵌入消除了虚假的映射先验，从而实现了稳健的上下文检索。作为一个单一的统一模型，VAP 在开源方法中设立了新的标杆，用户偏好率达到38.7%，可与领先的条件特定商业模型媲美。VAP 的强大零样本泛化能力和对各种下游应用的支持标志着向通用、可控视频生成的重大进步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/video-as-prompt\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/video-as-prompt</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：MiniOneRec</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"234\" data-imgfileid=\"100016794\" data-ratio=\"0.20092592592592592\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa8550aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXSGAIeiatOiajozNgUxQF6rK6Zlbiae0Cpw4YjPqqd2jUV09D6pr7DcJjWLDohFT8wiaicQUYz0NbUzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MiniOneRec是首个完全开源的生成式推荐框架，提供从SID构建、监督微调到推荐导向的强化学习的端到端工作流程。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在通过生成式推荐技术提升推荐系统的性能，结合大语言模型的世界知识和离散项目代码，实现高效的推荐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/minionerec\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/minionerec</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：ScaleNet</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"584\" data-imgfileid=\"100016792\" data-ratio=\"0.5009259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d836e84a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXSGAIeiatOiajozNgUxQF6ruzJNNGb3u8kJvo6SicBf1Gn7dS4psia67XLfUcpotwZux2ZJJCJoZkWA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ScaleNet是一种高效扩展视觉Transformer（ViT）模型的方法。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与传统的从头训练不同，ScaleNet通过在预训练的ViT模型中插入额外层来实现模型扩展，同时利用层次权重共享以保持参数效率。为了减轻潜在的性能下降，ScaleNet为每层引入了一小组调整参数，通过并行适配器模块实现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/scalenet2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/scalenet2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：flash-moba</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"382\" data-imgfileid=\"100016790\" data-ratio=\"0.3277777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=29f8da57&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXSGAIeiatOiajozNgUxQF6rXukEcbptOOM2bbMf6G9xOibbl6SBQsUE0SP737OXiaYUwyfOop1BJnpw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FlashMoBA 是一种内存高效的稀疏注意力机制，旨在加速长序列模型的训练和推理。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了 FlashMoBA 的官方实现，基于 FlashAttention 2.8.3，并受到 MoBA 的启发。FlashMoBA 通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">优化块注意力的混合</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来提高计算效率，特别适用于处理变长序列，避免了在填充标记上的计算浪费。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/flash-moba\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/flash-moba</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：CudaForge</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"484\" data-imgfileid=\"100016788\" data-ratio=\"0.4148148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d268c41&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXSGAIeiatOiajozNgUxQF6rNI7HKAASicbNdBwG9hdYuSJLMiaB0dKQGVhB0J4PNG4hV9bicOzXDjfGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★CudaForge是一个用于CUDA内核生成和优化的Agent框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目不需要训练，灵感来源于人类专家的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">迭代工作流程</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，包括开发初始内核、测试正确性、分析硬件反馈和迭代改进等步骤。通过多Agent的工作流，CudaForge能够自动化地进行内核优化，提升CUDA程序的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/cudaforge\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/cudaforge</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">&nbsp;Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：ReSeek</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"356\" data-imgfileid=\"100016786\" data-ratio=\"0.30648148148148147\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a8eec54a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzXSGAIeiatOiajozNgUxQF6rkO28mrJZnEzhFLQJX2ByHicfprXYmkI4v86RAia5ica8cnAg4b37zLicqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ReSeek是一个创新的强化学习框架，旨在通过自我纠正机制帮助搜索Agent在搜索过程中动态识别并纠正错误路径。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过特殊的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">JUDGE</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">动作，Agent可以评估检索到的信息并重新规划搜索策略。该框架设计了一种密集的指导性奖励函数，提供关于事实正确性和上下文实用性的细粒度反馈。ReSeek在多跳推理场景中表现尤为出色，展示了在复杂知识密集任务中的强大自我纠正能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/reseek3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/reseek3</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章汇集了字节跳动联合港中文推出的 Video As Prompt 可控视频生成模型、生成式推荐框架 MiniOneRec 等多个前沿 AI 开源项目，涵盖模型、框架和 Agent 开发。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章汇集了字节跳动联合港中文推出的 Video As Prompt 可控视频生成模型、生成式推荐框架 MiniOneRec 等多个前沿 AI 开源项目，涵盖模型、框架和 Agent 开发。",
  "summary": "本文“今日开源”栏目精选并介绍了多个最新的 AI 开源项目，旨在帮助技术从业者快速了解前沿动态。其中，字节跳动与香港中文大学联合推出的 Video-As-Prompt 是首个统一的语义视频生成模型，通过参考视频作为提示，利用混合变压器架构实现可控动画生成，用户偏好率高。MiniOneRec 则作为首个完全开源的生成式推荐框架，结合大语言模型和离散项目代码，旨在提升推荐系统性能。此外，文章还介绍了高效扩展视觉 Transformer 的 ScaleNet、内存高效稀疏注意力机制 FlashMoBA、用于 CUDA 内核生成和优化的 Agent 框架 CudaForge，以及通过自我纠正机制优化搜索 Agent 的强化学习框架 ReSeek。这些项目在各自领域都展现了创新性和实用价值，为 AI 研究和开发提供了新的工具和思路。",
